title: RHOBH: I Nose What You Did Last Season
description:
The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills is back, and there's so much to talk about: Crytal, Kathy, goldfish, Halloween injuries. We don't know where to start! Come join us!

Also, don't just listen to the recap, watch it too with Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/51461598/

Our Patreon Extras: https://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens
